			<h1><span class="data"></span><span class="vis"></span>DIY A Multiview Camera System:<br> <a href="http://domedb.perception.cs.cmu.edu">Panoptic Studio</a> Teardown<br>
			</h1>
			<span style="font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.5em;"><strong>Tutorial, <a href="http://cvpr2017.thecvf.com/">CVPR 2017</a></strong></span><br>
			<span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5em;">8:30 AM - 12:30 PM, July 21, Friday</span> <br>
			<span style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.5em;">Hawaii Convention Center, Room 303AB</span> <br>

		 
